莉莉·艾伦多年来因未回复信件而对埃尔顿·约翰“怀有很大的怨恨”——直到她意识到自己从未寄出这封信https://www.nme.com/news/music/lily-allen-resentment-elton-john-over-lack-of-reply-to-never-sent-letter-3754521?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=lily-艾伦对埃尔顿·约翰因未寄出的信未得到回复而不满Tom SkinnerWed, 08 May 2024 14:09:58 +0000 Music NewsNewsPopRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3754521 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/LilyAllen-Elton-John-letter-story.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="艾尔顿·约翰和莉莉·艾伦 2008 年合影" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/LilyAllen-Elton-John-letter-story.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/LilyAllen-Elton-John-letter-story-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/LilyAllen-Elton-John-letter-story-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/LilyAllen-Elton-John-letter-story-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/LilyAllen-Elton-John-letter-story-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/LilyAllen-Elton-John-letter-story-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “你将永远是我生命中最伟大的酷儿偶像，”曾受《火箭人》明星管理的艾伦说道。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lily-allen-resentment-elton-john-over-lack-of-reply-to-never-sent-letter-3754521">莉莉·艾伦 (Lily Allen) 多年来因未回复信件而对埃尔顿·约翰 (Elton John) 的帖子“怀有很大的怨恨”，直到她意识到自己从未发送过该帖子，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/LilyAllen-Elton-John-letter-story.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="艾尔顿·约翰和莉莉·艾伦 2008 年合影" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/LilyAllen-Elton-John-letter-story.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/LilyAllen-Elton-John-letter-story-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/LilyAllen-Elton-John-letter-story-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/LilyAllen-Elton-John-letter-story-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/LilyAllen-Elton-John-letter-story-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/LilyAllen-Elton-John-letter-story-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lily-allen">莉莉·艾伦</a>透露，她多年来一直对<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/elton-john">埃尔顿·约翰</a>怀恨在心，因为他没有回复她的信，直到意识到她实际上并没有寄出这封信。</p><p>在她最近一集<a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0hp4s75" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《想念我吗？》</em></a>中在 Miquita Oliver 的播客（5 月 6 日发布）中，艾伦回忆起自己曾经“由埃尔顿·约翰 (Elton John) 旗下的一家管理公司管理”和他的丈夫大卫·弗尼什 (David Furnish)。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/lily-allen-big-read-interview-2018-2334656">《 <em>NME</em>大读物》——莉莉·艾伦：“我正在掌控我的叙述”</a></strong></li></ul><p>当她制作和宣传她的第二张录音室专辑 2009 年的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/reviews-lily-allen-10076-340817">《It&#39;s Not Me, It&#39;s You》</a>时，这位歌手兼演员就在<a href="https://www.eltonjohn.com/rocket-entertainment" target="_blank" rel="noopener">火箭音乐娱乐集团的</a>名单上。</p><p> “我喜欢被他们管理，”艾伦解释道。 “每年埃尔顿都会举办圣诞派对，我总是坐在他旁边，他会让我感觉很特别。”</p><p>她继续说道：“他会每隔几周给我打电话一次，询问我的情况并打个招呼，并确保我一切都好。在那段时间里，有些时候我的状态不太好。”</p><p>艾伦接着回忆起，在她“生活不健康”的时期，埃尔顿爵士如何将<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/daily-gossip-568-1332014">她送到他位于法国南部的家中</a>“放松一下，晾干一点”。</p><p>这位“LDN”艺术家随后回顾了她如何在 2014 年发行第三张专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/reviews-lily-allen-15280-310827">“Sheezus”</a>后“与这位传奇创作歌手“分道扬镳”。</p><p> “我对此感到非常难过，”艾伦透露。 “我给埃尔顿写了这封长信，表达我对这种情况感到多么难过，而且我特别难过，因为他不再给我打电话了，我也没有接到埃尔顿每两个月打来的电话来报到。我的生活中出现了一个埃尔顿形的大洞。”</p><p>艾伦说：“在接下来的几年里，当我的生活开始失控时，我对自己在这封信中让自己变得非常脆弱并向他讲述了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lily-allen-says-her-life-has-changed-so-much-after-four-years-of-sobriety-3423061">我清醒的</a>一切感到非常不满。</p><p> “埃尔顿，他是一个清醒的人，所以我认为他会回复这封信。几年来，我因为没有回复这封信而对他很生气，因为我一直很脆弱和开放。事实上，我认为他这样做很卑鄙。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C6njGG-opXp/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C565.244,65.022 564.756,66.606 564.346,67.663 C563.803,69.06 563.154,70.05