e-3754423">关闭，开发项目被废弃，工作人员被放开</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上首先<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/hades-2-surprise-early-access-release-has-been-a-hit-3754458">出现了“ Hades 2”惊喜早期访问发布</a>。</p> ;
